{"tid":1591720,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《掃毒2》代表香港報名奧斯卡最佳外語片","createTime":"2019-09-24T09:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T12:03:07.000Z","uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"1afb0aa0d7aff6b5c924cbe2946198b252f240eb","tid":1591720,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"(轉貼: <a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2458428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2458428&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=676e3ada\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2458428</a> )<br />\n「香港電影製片家協會」董事局按照「美國電影學院」角逐「奧斯卡最佳外語片」之選片準則，決定推薦由邱禮濤導演執導，寰宇娛樂有限公司、廣東昇格 傳媒股份有限公司出品，銀都機構有限公司、映藝娛樂有限公司、太陽娛樂文化 有限公司及北京合瑞影業文化有限公司聯合出品之電影《掃毒 2 天地對決》，代表香港角逐「第 92 屆奧斯卡金像獎最佳外語片獎」。<br />\n<br />\n是次推選，製片家協會董事局成員由 2018 年 10 月份至 2019 年 9 月份期間上映之所有香港電影中挑選，當中《掃毒 2 天地對決》佔大多數票當選提名代表 香港參加角逐第 92 屆奧斯卡最佳外語片。<br />\n<br />\n近10年香港代表報名電影:<br />\n2009 淚王子<br />\n2010 歲月神偷<br />\n2011 桃姐 <br />\n2012 奪命金 <br />\n2013 一代宗師<br />\n2014 黄金時代 <br />\n2015 破風 <br />\n2016 踏血尋梅 <br />\n2017 一念無明  <br />\n2018 紅海行動<br />\n2019 掃毒 2 天地對決"},{"pid":"ce7f4d4ec93c39d762a190b5ce561bb5272e66e8","tid":1591720,"uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"For your consideration:<br />\nBest Original Song: 兄弟不懷疑<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=beaYy7T9zdI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbeaYy7T9zdI&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=54652176\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=beaYy7T9zdI</a>"},{"pid":"f6950d2492af148cbb0c34794633771f496a3b1a","tid":1591720,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\